<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - J.C. Penney estimates cut.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - J.C. Penney estimates cut.</headline>
<text>
<p>- Rodman &amp; Renshaw Inc said Tuesday it lowered its fiscal first quarter earnings estimates for J.C. Penney Co Inc to $0.50 a share from $0.54, and its fiscal second quarter estimate to $0.37 from $0.40.</p>
<p>- &quot;We estimate department store sales are trending below plan with total stores about flat for the month and comparable store sales down one percent,&quot; Rodman &amp; Renshaw said in a release.</p>
<p>- Shares of J.C. Penney were off 3/8 at 47-1/4.</p>
<p>((--Chicago newsdesk, 312-408-8787))</p>
